snippet.title: Sandy hook 911 Operator says Shooting FAKE in background

localized.description:
update - Michael Rivero cleaned up the section where FAKE is said - it is on this video 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4aewBp62rIg&feature=youtu.be
I go through tape 2 of the Sandy Hook 911 call.  This is where Rick Thorne first calls.  A 911 operator 'Jen' in the background of the 911 center says "Sandy Hook is Fake" in a questioning and disbelief tone.   I show where none of it make sense.  No wonder they didn't want the calls released, because the 911 operator announces it is fake.

Cleaned up section done by Michael Rivero from WhatReallyHappened.com
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4aewBp62rIg&feature=youtu.be

Another tape doesn't make sense - tape 4 - the woman who had her foot shot.  How is does NOT make any sense.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H5XoVX9EcSo&feature=youtu.be

http://sherriequestioningall.blogspot.com/2013/12/tape-2-of-sandy-hook-911-calls-woman-in.html
